snippet.textDisplay: I met this very sad and depressed and broken guy who went through a lot and as a Psychology student, I assessed him and became close friends eventually. He was starting to change and its very much evident by the way he perceive the little things in life. Secretly, throughout  the process I thought its just his braveness that I liked about him not knowing it was actually his overall self that I loved. Now he's a dad and  engaged to a very beautiful woman who made him a whole again as a person. I genuinely wish him the best.
